<item>
            <title>[FLINK-30814] The parallelism&amp;maxParallelism of sort after a global partitioning is not forced to be 1</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-30814</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The parallelism&amp;amp;maxParallelism of sort after a global partitioning is not forced to be 1. The may lead to the parallelism to be changed by adaptive batch scheduler, which is unexpected.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13521895">FLINK-30814</key>
            <summary>The parallelism&amp;maxParallelism of sort after a global partitioning is not forced to be 1</summary>
